<H2>AddFont</H2>
<H4 CLASS="st">Informations</H4>Author: <A HREF="&#109;ailto:axl63800&#64;wanadoo.fr?subject=AddFont">Yann Sugere</A><BR>License: Freeware
<H4 CLASS="st">Description</H4>This script allows to add new fonts to FPDF (for an easier usage of makefont.php). It works
on Windows and supported fonts are TrueType and Type1.<BR>
See readme.txt for installation and usage information.
